info.name: Google Search Cards Dark
info.description:
NOTE: THIS DOES NOT DO MUCH ON IT'S OWN! COMBINE WITH DARKSEARCH FOR GOOGLE OR SIMILAR!

This fixes the hideos white boxes Google have stuck under search results. Use this style in conjunction with an old dark theme to get it to look good.
info.additionalInfo: Install with Google DarkSearch for best results. Doesn't get rid of the thin white line at the top unfortunately.
